      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesnt feel like stress. it feels like... permanent. like the version of me that actually cared about stuff is just gone. i'm just a ghost pretending to be a person so i dont have to explain why i'm so empty. it's just so exhausting to keep up the act when there's nothing actually there",
